rows.label: qst650405_0010
rows.name: There!

rows.label: qst650405_0020
rows.name: There they are!

rows.label: qst650405_0030
rows.name: Found you at last.

rows.label: qst650405_0040
rows.name:
Hibana?
Let's try not to mess this up again, all right?

rows.label: qst650405_0050
rows.name: Fine, I get it...

rows.label: qst650405_0060
rows.name: No running in alone this time, promise...

rows.label: qst650405_0070
rows.name: We'll see about that.

rows.label: qst650405_0080
rows.name:
Three dogsbodies...one bossman...
And a Blade...

rows.label: qst650405_0090
rows.name:
Looks like they've beefed up the security.
They've got this place locked down.

rows.label: qst650405_0100
rows.name: All right. What approach would you suggest, then...?

rows.label: qst650405_0110
rows.name:
Well, for one thing, they've nowhere to run.
Let's hit 'em first and hit 'em hard.

rows.label: qst650405_0120
rows.name: I like that plan!

rows.label: qst650405_0130
rows.name: Well, no surprises there...

rows.label: qst650405_0140
rows.name: Hey, I thought it over carefully!

rows.label: qst650405_0150
rows.name: I cannot recommend that course.

rows.label: qst650405_0160
rows.name: Why's that?

rows.label: qst650405_0170
rows.name:
We're in the open.
No matter our speed, it's pointless.

rows.label: qst650405_0180
rows.name:
The instant they catch sight of us,
they can move on the children.

rows.label: qst650405_0190
rows.name: I bet they would, the louts.

rows.label: qst650405_0200
rows.name:
Hmm...
Are we sure about that?

rows.label: qst650405_0210
rows.name:
They see them as nothing but food.
Whether they're alive or dead, it makes no difference.

rows.label: qst650405_0220
rows.name: So what *do* we do?

rows.label: qst650405_0230
rows.name: Could we lure them away somehow?

rows.label: qst650405_0240
rows.name:
Their leader knew to post sentries at strategic locations...
They seem too disciplined to fall for it.

rows.label: qst650405_0250
rows.name: Agreed.

rows.label: qst650405_0260
rows.name: Hikari, could you take that one?

rows.label: qst650405_0270
rows.name:
I've run the ballistics, but no.
He's too close to the children.

rows.label: qst650405_0280
rows.name: Oh, right...

rows.label: qst650405_0290
rows.name:
I've had it!
If you think you can eat me, you're dead wrong!

rows.label: qst650405_0300
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Adlib getting punched out.

rows.label: qst650405_0310
rows.name: How could you...?!

rows.label: qst650405_0320
rows.name: Hey, now hold on...

rows.label: qst650405_0330
rows.name: I can't just stand here and watch!

rows.label: qst650405_0340
rows.name: Same old, same old...

rows.label: qst650405_0350
rows.name: I guess we're all going then!

rows.label: qst650405_0360
rows.name: Take this...!

rows.label: qst650405_0370
rows.name: Hibana!

rows.label: qst650405_0380
rows.name:
Oh no, I'm sorry!
Looks like I did it again...

rows.label: qst650405_0390
rows.name:
Nah, don't worry too much.
And look, you did manage to give us a way in.

rows.label: qst650405_0400
rows.name: Yes, it was a most clever distraction.

rows.label: qst650405_0410
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]adlib happy reaction

rows.label: qst650405_0420
rows.name:
And anyway, it's not like I wouldn't
have done the exact same thing, y'know?

rows.label: qst650405_0430
rows.name: Oh, my hero...

rows.label: qst650405_0440
rows.name:
There's no time to waste.
Let's get these children back home!

rows.label: qst650405_0450
rows.name: Yeah!
